Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.42,0:00:06.34,Default,Owl Woman,0,0,0,,最近老是下雨 真麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.41,0:00:08.18,Default,Owl Man,0,0,0,,只是下雨就不错了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.18,0:00:11.24,Default,Owl Man,0,0,0,,我这边最近可是全在下鲭鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.92,0:00:14.79,Default,Owl Man,0,0,0,,不管是烤还是煮都吃腻了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.79,0:00:18.48,Default,Owl Woman,0,0,0,,青鱼啊 喜欢还是讨厌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.37,0:00:26.35,Default,Owl Woman,0,0,0,,电车？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.89,0:00:28.77,Default,Owl Man,0,0,0,,怎么可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.77,0:00:32.36,Default,Owl Man,0,0,0,,现在还在运营的只有池巴士罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.65,0:00:45.08,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,好快好快好快！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.08,0:00:46.44,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留 冷静点！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.62,0:00:49.75,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,Go go go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.52,0:00:52.61,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,慢点！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.61,0:00:55.03,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,池袋站是港湾式站台！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.03,0:00:57.56,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶？港湾式站台是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.04,0:01:06.81,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这里是池袋吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.10,0:01:08.78,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我还以为要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.78,0:01:09.67,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.67,0:01:10.99,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,有受伤吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.99,0:01:12.13,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,但是我们做到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.13,0:01:14.28,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,终于到达池袋了！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.69,0:01:19.28,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,所谓的港湾式站台 就是像这样的尽头…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.43,0:01:21.88,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,波奇 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.56,0:01:24.90,Default,Leader,0,0,0,,发现侵入者！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.90,0:01:25.79,Default,Leader,0,0,0,,消灭他们！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.79,0:01:27.37,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶？突然搞什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.37,0:01:28.90,Default,Leader,0,0,0,,攻击！前进！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.90,0:01:30.81,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不由分说吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.15,0:01:36.93,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,叶香的味道？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.93,0:01:37.78,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,走吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.78,0:01:38.73,Default,Group,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.73,0:01:40.13,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,等等我！
