Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.75,0:03:14.55,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,您醒了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.55,0:03:16.95,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,饭已经准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.55,0:03:22.69,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.34,0:03:26.64,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,今天吃什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.91,0:03:31.59,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,竹荚鱼干、嫩蛋蘑菇和苦瓜味噌汤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.08,0:03:33.36,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,{\an8}好像很好吃
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.14,0:03:37.65,Signs_WText,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,1020)\bord0.6\pos(1307.664,778.67)}{\fs98}第{\fs103}11{\fs}{\fs98}话    已经不行了吧{\fs70\fn獅尾圓體SC-Regular}……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.89,0:03:36.68,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,{\an8}之前是不是也吃过苦瓜来着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.68,0:03:38.47,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,{\an8}你喜欢苦瓜吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.47,0:03:41.27,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,不 不是这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.27,0:03:43.02,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,叶香大人您讨厌苦瓜吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.66,0:03:45.24,Default,Pochi,0,1200,0,,讨厌的话 之后就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.50,0:03:46.39,Yoka,Yoka,600,0,0,,不 并不是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.39,0:03:48.88,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,只是有种奇怪的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.59,0:03:51.12,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,奇怪的感觉？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.58,0:03:53.63,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.63,0:03:57.58,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,明明没怎么吃过 但不知为何感到怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.58,0:03:59.13,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,所以才奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.13,0:04:00.04,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.96,0:04:03.82,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,这个产自哪里来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.36,0:04:05.22,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.06,0:04:09.02,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.95,0:04:14.84,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊 有人在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.12,0:04:16.69,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,问下那个人吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.05,0:04:18.20,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,打扰了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.20,0:04:19.69,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,稍微占用你几分钟！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.21,0:04:23.62,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我们在找一个叫中富叶香的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.02,0:04:27.88,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,呜哇 好大的大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.88,0:04:28.83,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,厨房围裙？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:29.86,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,要讲礼貌！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.21,0:04:35.04,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶？怎么了怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.05,0:04:37.16,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,有什么事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.16,0:04:39.60,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,又是那个叫金太郎的人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.25,0:04:45.85,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,叶…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:09.11,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,真可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.92,0:05:11.48,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,这是你的狗吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.48,0:05:13.46,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,我以前也养过狗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.46,0:05:15.05,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,一只叫波奇的狗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.05,0:05:17.20,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,你的名字是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.80,0:05:20.86,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,不对！这就是波奇啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.86,0:05:22.40,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,你怎么看不出来呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.40,0:05:25.93,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,大家从吾野来接叶香你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.93,0:05:27.78,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,你是叶香吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.04,0:05:41.32,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,你们 是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.10,0:05:44.44,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,难道说 你还在生气？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:48.45,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,生什么的气？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.90,0:05:51.41,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,为什么我要生气？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.41,0:05:52.29,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.09,0:06:11.77,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,突然…有种不好的感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.50,0:06:15.16,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,胸口里面好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.16,0:06:16.40,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,等等 叶香
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.40,0:06:18.40,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,你不记得我们了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:20.22,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,骗人吧！记忆丧失？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.22,0:06:23.54,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,她像善治郎先生那样 做了喵喵手术吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.54,0:06:24.57,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,怎么这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.61,0:06:30.62,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,我是中富叶香
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.12,0:06:33.33,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,喜欢天文学的高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.75,0:06:36.62,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,在池袋每天认真学习
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.09,0:06:38.44,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,学习很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.44,0:06:40.56,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,了解未知很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.90,0:06:42.57,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,因为世界很广阔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.57,0:06:44.86,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,然后 将来的梦想是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.38,0:06:49.24,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,将来的…梦想是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:50.34,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,叶——
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.48,0:06:54.35,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.51,0:06:56.94,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,叶香？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.49,0:07:01.72,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,叶香大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.72,0:07:03.10,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,请冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.10,0:07:05.15,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,我是中富叶香…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.15,0:07:06.30,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,听我说 叶香！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.30,0:07:07.14,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那个啊——
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.75,0:07:09.48,Default,Vigilante,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.17,0:07:13.55,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,居然这么快就找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.55,0:07:16.41,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,意图伤害公主的烦人虫子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.41,0:07:18.57,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,竟敢与我们的叶香公主同席
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.57,0:07:20.79,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,何等蛮不讲理之徒！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:22.13,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,也就是说 是敌人！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.13,0:07:23.21,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,击溃她们！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.34,0:07:25.44,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,换句话说 打她们个落花流水！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.44,0:07:26.84,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,不好 要死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:28.08,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,感觉要死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.08,0:07:28.93,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,叶香！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.93,0:07:30.46,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,等等 叶香！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.46,0:07:31.98,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留 现在不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.98,0:07:32.91,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,大家 这边走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.91,0:07:34.99,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,死了的话 之前就白费功夫了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.09,0:07:39.10,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,公主！您玉体无恙吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:39.80,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.75,0:07:47.54,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,这么重要的东西怎么能放在这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.54,0:07:48.39,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,你这鸟脑子！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.39,0:07:50.06,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.06,0:07:51.20,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,是她们…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:52.07,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,肯定没错！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:53.89,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,就是因为她们公主才…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.89,0:07:55.69,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,抓住她们！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.69,0:07:57.79,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,绝对别让她们逃掉了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.01,0:07:59.91,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,好 动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.21,0:08:01.36,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,动啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.36,0:08:03.74,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,快快快！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.80,0:08:09.54,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,怎么就让她们逃掉了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.01,0:08:13.02,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,我要上报公主 将你们全部处以心太之刑！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.00,0:08:15.60,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,坏了 不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.60,0:08:19.51,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,考虑到按钮和公主的反应 最好把她们分开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.51,0:08:21.22,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,我还以为已经足够警惕了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.22,0:08:23.22,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,我太天真了 混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.18,0:08:28.36,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,有何贵干？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.76,0:08:30.69,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,什么「有何贵干」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.69,0:08:31.98,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,你这大笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.98,0:08:34.29,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,我们把公主转移到其他地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.50,0:08:35.05,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.05,0:08:36.93,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,因为你放走的那些人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.93,0:08:38.86,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,可能会再来夺走公主！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.86,0:08:40.85,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,这种事都无法理解吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.14,0:08:43.88,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,公主本人可能不会同意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.88,0:08:46.47,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,她很喜欢那个房间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.47,0:08:48.84,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,谁在意她喜不喜欢啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.22,0:08:51.81,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,还是说你觉得自己能保护好公主吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.81,0:08:52.89,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.89,0:08:56.71,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,如果他们伤到公主一根毫毛 你就等着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.71,0:08:57.46,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.46,0:08:58.63,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,给我准备搬运车！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.63,0:09:00.01,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,还有警卫！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.14,0:09:05.60,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,那人有没有可能不是叶香啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.60,0:09:06.45,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.45,0:09:07.68,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,毕竟很可疑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.14,0:09:09.38,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,那么奇怪的叶香
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.96,0:09:12.24,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,都认不出我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.68,0:09:14.93,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,确实很奇怪 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.36,0:09:17.45,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我觉得那就是叶香
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:19.95,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,说的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.95,0:09:22.75,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,波奇也觉得那是叶香呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.75,0:09:24.50,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,肯定是叶香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:27.44,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,所以叶香那样是非常生气了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.70,0:09:28.95,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,绝交级别的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.95,0:09:30.16,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,绝交什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.54,0:09:31.81,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.81,0:09:34.81,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,如果我是叶香的话 也会绝交的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.16,0:09:37.85,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶？怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.56,0:09:41.38,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,这是摩斯啊 摩斯电码！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.38,0:09:43.36,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,是善治郎先生和诚老师！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.68,0:09:45.52,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,为什么是通过苦瓜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.02,0:09:49.18,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,可能是通过从吾野长到这的藤蔓和根来连接的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.58,0:09:50.32,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.32,0:09:52.55,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,从吾野 到这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.30,0:09:55.20,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,苦瓜最强！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.74,0:09:57.89,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,所以诚老师说了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.89,0:09:59.89,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,「横切苦瓜」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.89,0:10:00.43,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.43,0:10:02.08,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留 菜刀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.86,0:10:06.12,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,测试 测试
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.24,0:10:08.13,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.13,0:10:10.64,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,苦瓜里传出了诚老师的声音！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.64,0:10:12.96,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,好奇怪的日语
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.90,0:10:17.05,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,别烦了！听得见！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.05,0:10:18.66,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,是诚老师！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.96,0:10:21.87,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,喂！看得见吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.87,0:10:24.07,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,看不见 这是声音专用的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.07,0:10:25.01,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.01,0:10:27.67,Default,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,弄明白将世界变回去的方法了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.67,0:10:28.90,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶？你谁啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.90,0:10:30.38,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,是善治郎先生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.38,0:10:31.66,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,弄明白是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.66,0:10:35.66,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,还没有实证 只是可信度很高的假设
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.14,0:10:39.82,Default,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,作为7G开通起点的开关 是个按钮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.20,0:10:42.62,Default,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,那个按钮一直处于开启的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.00,0:10:45.66,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,就是说 如果再按一次按钮将其关闭的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.66,0:10:46.37,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,的话？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.72,0:10:48.65,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,7G的回路就会被切断
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.65,0:10:50.93,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,电波的影响也会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.57,0:10:53.93,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,就是说 可能会变回以前的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.86,0:10:55.88,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,这样就行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:10:56.90,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,不不不！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.90,0:10:58.16,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,这也太简单了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.16,0:11:00.04,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,因此我们忽视了它
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.20,0:11:03.09,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,我们太过忙于处理单个现象
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.09,0:11:06.16,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,导致没有思考停止根本诱因的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.16,0:11:07.79,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,也许是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.79,0:11:09.81,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,那个按钮在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.81,0:11:11.11,Default,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.11,0:11:13.90,Default,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,至少 如果我是毒太郎的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.90,0:11:16.37,Default,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,我会把它置于严格的警备中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.81,0:11:21.84,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,在维持现状与回到过去的争纷中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.84,0:11:24.50,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,按钮的存在决定了双方的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.01,0:11:27.52,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,我一旦有新情报就联系你们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.84,0:11:30.88,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,记得把通过话的苦瓜好好吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.26,0:11:31.99,Default,Group,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.99,0:11:34.50,Default,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,不要浪费食…帽帽帽帽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.28,0:11:37.38,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,嗯？是平时的善治郎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.38,0:11:42.85,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,虽然最近把反帽帽模式延长到了5分38秒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.85,0:11:44.12,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,这不是很厉害吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.12,0:11:47.15,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,不 离完全的反帽帽还远得很
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.38,0:11:49.71,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,像这样继续延长的话 能变回原样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.71,0:11:52.28,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,计算得出还要94年
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.88,0:11:55.02,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.41,0:11:56.98,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,得想想办法才行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.98,0:12:00.54,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,94年之后善治郎先生已经死了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.54,0:12:01.76,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,不是在说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.76,0:12:03.19,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是在说按钮对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.62,0:12:07.47,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,也就是说 存在「核足球」一样的东西吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.47,0:12:08.74,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,啥？ 你说的是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.74,0:12:11.87,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,就是总统用来发射核兵器的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.87,0:12:13.82,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,他的保镖将其贴身携带 寸步不离
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.82,0:12:15.19,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,那不是很危险吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.19,0:12:17.02,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,要是被偷了怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.02,0:12:19.93,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,虽然这种情节在小说和电影里都快被写烂了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.93,0:12:21.70,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,但从未在现实中发生过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.70,0:12:22.31,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,你们说…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.31,0:12:24.37,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,叶香的态度变得那么冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.37,0:12:26.32,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,会不会就是因为那个按钮？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.32,0:12:27.31,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.31,0:12:29.90,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,如果说世界因为按下按钮而改变
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.90,0:12:31.81,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,那么只要再按一次按钮将它关闭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.81,0:12:33.98,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,说不定世界和叶香都会恢复原状
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.98,0:12:35.37,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 这样啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.37,0:12:37.69,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,所以她看上去才那么不对劲呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.69,0:12:38.76,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.76,0:12:39.84,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,真是这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.84,0:12:42.06,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,也只能这么想了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.06,0:12:43.16,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,你也太头脑简单了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.16,0:12:44.35,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,人是会变的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.35,0:12:45.52,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,但也不是没可能嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.52,0:12:46.89,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我想要找到按钮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.22,0:12:50.70,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,只要有这个可能 就该尝试一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.97,0:12:52.69,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我觉得很好 赞成！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.69,0:12:53.44,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.44,0:12:55.63,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,晶你又在那犹犹豫豫了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.63,0:12:56.51,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,你先听我说！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.51,0:12:58.09,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,当然可以去找按钮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:12:59.92,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,但是 怎样才找得到呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.92,0:13:03.08,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,寻找和到手可是不同的任务啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:09.73,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.73,0:13:11.22,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,是僵尸们？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.56,0:13:14.98,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,这不是黑木木嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.35,0:13:16.65,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,你怎么来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.18,0:13:18.66,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.97,0:13:23.48,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,和你们分别后 保谷站附近的环境变化越发极端
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.48,0:13:26.96,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,如果继续待在那里 僵尸全都会腐烂发霉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.96,0:13:28.83,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,或是干燥龟裂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.06,0:13:31.75,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,僵尸原来这么纤弱呀 真意外
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.75,0:13:34.00,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,所以你想跟我们携手合作？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.48,0:13:36.78,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,我们有着数量上的优势
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.78,0:13:39.51,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,你们则有…头脑？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.51,0:13:40.62,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,为什么是疑问句？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.62,0:13:43.60,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,头脑担当的诚老师 刚刚跟我们说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.60,0:13:47.77,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,找到停止7G的按钮的话 说不定能做点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.77,0:13:49.57,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,头脑担当是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.57,0:13:51.44,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,你就是肌肉担当吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.44,0:13:53.28,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,那个按钮在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.28,0:13:54.36,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我们也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.36,0:13:57.81,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,但是 既然它有将世界变成这样的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.81,0:13:59.52,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,想必相当大吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.52,0:14:01.74,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,就像酒桶一样？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.74,0:14:03.09,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,酒桶？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.09,0:14:03.94,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.94,0:14:04.68,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.68,0:14:07.22,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,我们从百货商场的边上经过时
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.97,0:14:11.98,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,怎么了？ 发生什么事了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.98,0:14:22.62,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,僵尸对脑髓和花椰菜之外的东西生起了兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.94,0:14:25.50,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,僵尸们渴望重新变回人类
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.50,0:14:31.46,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,它们也许就是感知到了\N拥有将它们变回原样的力量的按钮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:34.65,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,那很有可能就是我们在找的按钮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.65,0:14:36.88,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,什么？ 也有可能不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.88,0:14:38.44,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,你说那座百货商场呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.44,0:14:39.83,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我没去过诶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.83,0:14:40.49,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.49,0:14:42.21,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,「时髦的生活」对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.21,0:14:43.88,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,还有「最爱自己」对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:46.73,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,以前看过这样的广告 我一直都很向往
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.73,0:14:47.88,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,你是说你想去？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.88,0:14:49.98,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,可是 我们好不容易能来一次池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.98,0:14:51.42,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,去看看也没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.52,0:14:53.37,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,你只是单纯地想去百货商场吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:54.63,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,想去购物对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.63,0:14:56.27,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,去百货商场只是顺路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.27,0:14:57.82,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,当然按钮也要找啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.82,0:14:58.78,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,满口谎言！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.78,0:15:01.15,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,那个叫毒太郎的应该会把它藏起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.15,0:15:02.82,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,感觉他总在摆架子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.08,0:15:04.89,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,波伊森·毒太郎吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.89,0:15:06.98,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,我只听说过他很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.98,0:15:09.94,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,善治郎先生也说过他是屎中屎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.94,0:15:12.06,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,说是只考虑自己的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.64,0:15:15.56,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,说到底他应该与7G有关吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:18.64,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,可是他居然不想让世界恢复原状\N还一副趾高气扬的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.64,0:15:22.35,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,那当然是因为他不想负起\N把世界变得一团糟的责任吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.35,0:15:25.24,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,明明是自己犯错却不承担责任 太差劲了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.38,0:15:28.82,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,原来如此 就像作为贬义词的僵尸那样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:29.40,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.73,0:15:32.96,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,视野狭窄 只能考虑眼前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.96,0:15:34.49,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,既不反省过去 也不展望未来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.94,0:15:36.22,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.22,0:15:37.96,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.96,0:15:39.12,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不对 可能有事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.12,0:15:40.86,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,怎么办？要去百货商场吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.86,0:15:41.74,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我要去我要去！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.74,0:15:43.59,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,那叶香要怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.59,0:15:44.92,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,已经不行了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.92,0:15:45.69,Default,Group,0,0,0,,哈？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.69,0:15:47.01,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,什么不行了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.01,0:15:48.44,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,毕竟我们已经绝交了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.44,0:15:50.07,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,你又在说这话了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.07,0:15:51.56,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我说呀 静留
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.56,0:15:53.95,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,现在还说这种话我会很困扰的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.95,0:15:55.43,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,抚子 你好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.43,0:15:57.38,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我想去见叶香
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.38,0:15:59.19,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,就算你不想见她 我也会去！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.19,0:16:00.79,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我也想！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.79,0:16:02.14,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,你是想去百货商场吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.14,0:16:02.98,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,才不是啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.98,0:16:04.23,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,好吗 静留？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.23,0:16:05.98,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,有什么好不好的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.98,0:16:08.20,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,就算静留你不想去见她 我也会让你们见面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.20,0:16:08.85,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.65,0:16:10.56,Default,Group,0,0,0,,什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.62,0:16:21.88,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,看来只好来一场地毯式搜索了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.88,0:16:23.08,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,为什么要说得这么夸张？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.08,0:16:26.44,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,因为从前我可没想过\N会在现实中说出「地毯式搜索」这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.44,0:16:27.13,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.13,0:16:30.50,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,就和「你这偷腥猫！」「你安心上路吧！」一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.50,0:16:33.35,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,我也想说一次「你眼瞎了吗？」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.35,0:16:35.37,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,噢！ 黑木木你很懂嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.37,0:16:38.32,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,人生中未曾说出口的台词 有很多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.32,0:16:40.44,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,未曾说出口的台词…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.51,0:16:43.73,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,你得去告诉她呀 静留
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.81,0:16:45.65,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.11,0:16:53.88,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.88,0:16:55.37,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,也许是找到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.11,0:17:01.95,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,把这些收拾掉！快！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.21,0:17:04.20,Default,Employee A,0,0,0,,您有什么想要的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.20,0:17:06.02,Default,Employee A,0,0,0,,这个很受欢迎的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.02,0:17:07.13,Default,Employee A,0,0,0,,非常适合您
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.13,0:17:08.93,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,唔 我讨厌这个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.93,0:17:10.57,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,用微笑上压力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.94,0:17:11.79,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,而且还变多了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.79,0:17:13.29,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,就算逃跑也会追上来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.29,0:17:14.38,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,现在就该用那一招！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.38,0:17:16.97,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,我就看看！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.22,0:17:23.68,Default,Painting,0,0,0,,世界级著名艺术品
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.77,0:17:24.43,Default,Painting,0,0,0,,{\an8}允许分期付款
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.68,0:17:25.91,Default,Painting,0,0,0,,国宝级大师绘制
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.86,0:17:26.93,Default,Painting,0,0,0,,{\an8}过了这村就没这店
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.93,0:17:27.65,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,碍事！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.65,0:17:29.70,Default,Group,0,0,0,,你赔偿得起吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.70,0:17:32.56,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,谁会赔你啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.93,0:17:35.60,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,别想骗我们掏钱！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.45,0:17:39.35,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,僵尸们有反应了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.35,0:17:40.29,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,是按钮吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.29,0:17:41.38,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.38,0:17:43.66,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,百货商场里出现了可疑的团伙？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.66,0:17:46.29,Default,Leader,0,0,0,,现在自警团正前去迎击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.29,0:17:48.42,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,她们果然是瞄着按钮来的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.42,0:17:50.69,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,不对 她们怎么知道按钮在哪里的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.50,0:17:53.75,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,难道说我们有内奸吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.75,0:17:55.89,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,换句话说情报泄露了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.89,0:17:57.25,Default,Leader,0,0,0,,怎么可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.69,0:17:59.30,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,既然如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.72,0:18:03.18,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,你明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.49,0:18:05.12,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,你的使命是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.12,0:18:07.64,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,保护叶香大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.30,0:18:11.68,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,明白这个就去把那伙人解决掉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.68,0:18:13.94,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,然后扔到杂司谷的对面去！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.94,0:18:15.65,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,而且要保护好按钮！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.65,0:18:18.36,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,按钮被抢走的话 现在的世界就会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.36,0:18:21.59,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,民众会爆发愤怒 掀起暴动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.59,0:18:25.58,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,那样的话 你喜爱的叶香大人也会被波及
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.17,0:18:29.52,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,保护公主和保护按钮基本是一样的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.52,0:18:30.62,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,两者相等！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.62,0:18:32.97,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,绝不能让按钮被夺走！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.80,0:18:45.36,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,池子里有东西！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.36,0:18:46.24,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,是按钮！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.24,0:18:48.18,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,他们为什么对按钮起反应？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.18,0:18:50.72,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,他们也是7G引发的变化的产物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.72,0:18:54.45,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,能量上的共鸣 或者对原本世界的兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.45,0:18:55.77,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,像是这些 他们大概可以感受到什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.10,0:18:58.21,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,只要按下按钮就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.21,0:18:59.24,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.54,0:19:00.27,Default,Leader,0,0,0,,她们在这！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.27,0:19:01.16,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,又来？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.16,0:19:02.86,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,就由我来引开他们！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.86,0:19:04.43,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你们快去按按钮！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.76,0:19:04.74,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,{\an8}我也来帮忙！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.74,0:19:06.01,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,我们这边去回收按钮！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.12,0:19:16.95,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,僵尸不要踏进水里！会受潮的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.14,0:19:26.01,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.01,0:19:27.34,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,我是波奇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.63,0:19:28.63,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,波奇？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.12,0:19:29.99,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,波奇是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.75,0:19:35.45,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.45,0:19:37.11,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,我们怀有同样的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.11,0:19:38.05,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.05,0:19:39.40,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,保护叶香大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.01,0:19:53.33,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,叶香她…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.33,0:19:56.08,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,叶香她觉得现在这样是好的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.08,0:19:58.35,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,她每一天都在认真学习
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.35,0:19:59.35,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,但是！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.67,0:20:01.67,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,人们都说她是魔女！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.67,0:20:04.75,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,那不是叶香大人自己的问题！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.98,0:20:13.48,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,你怎么说都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.48,0:20:16.32,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,叶香大人只要做好她自己就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.29,0:20:26.25,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,玲实！静留！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.88,0:20:31.97,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,我们拿到按钮了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.97,0:20:32.99,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,按下去！按钮！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.99,0:20:34.60,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,快！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.02,0:20:50.51,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,停下了吗 7G？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.77,0:20:58.84,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,没用！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.84,0:20:59.57,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.14,0:21:01.52,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.00,0:21:06.09,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,僵尸35号！72号！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.09,0:21:06.97,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,躲远点！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.97,0:21:08.65,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,你们现在很危险！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.40,0:21:12.71,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.72,0:21:14.83,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,波奇 别过去…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.17,0:21:17.36,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,波奇…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.90,0:21:20.08,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,我不会与你战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.33,0:21:46.08,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.56,0:21:51.85,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,叶香！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.79,0:21:54.21,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,车上的是叶香？！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.06,0:21:56.56,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,一群蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.56,0:21:58.16,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,池袋会安定的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.02,0:22:00.67,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,只要公主还在
